Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=10}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:53.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:57.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Enel must've taken\Nthe golden bell by now. - Funi}{Enel's long gone with that\Ngolden bell by now. - Z}Enel provavelmente já está\Ncom aquele sino dourado.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:03.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If he took it, then I'll take it back! - Funi}Então eu vou ter que pegar de volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:05.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let me use this! - Funi}{Yoink}Estou pegando isso emprestado!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.83,0:02:24.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Até o Heaven's Gate... foi destruído\Nnum piscar de olhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:27.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{To think that Angel Island is gone... - Funi}Não acredito que Angel Island se foi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:30.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que vamos fazer agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:33.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In any case, we have to escape\Nto the Blue Sea via Cloud End! - Funi}Por agora, vamos ao Cloud End\Ne escapar pro Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não temos outra escolha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:39.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But there're still many people\Nleft in the White-White Sea! - Funi}Mas ainda tem tanta gente\Nno White-White Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What can we do?! - Funi}O que devemos fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:45.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/q2]How can we bring those ships down\Nto the White Sea without the milky roads?! - Funi}{\q2}As estradas lácteas sumiram, como vamos\Nlevar os navios até o White Sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:48.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then, are we giving up on them?! - Funi}Então vamos simplesmente abandoná-los?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:06.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even this area will be\Nlike that before long. - Funi}{It's not long before\Ndown here is trashed too. - Z}Não vai demorar até que\Neste lugar também seja destruído!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:12.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O White-White Sea está...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:18.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Skypiea está desaparecendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então é isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Splendid! - Funi}Magnífico!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:47.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/q2]So this is the grand belfry that was\Nthe pride of the legendary city, Shandora! - Funi}O glorioso sino, orgulho da\Nlendária cidade de Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:53.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is a perfect fit for me,\Nthe one who is God! - Funi}Como é apropriado que eu, Deus,\Npossua tal maravilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:58.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O sino que proclamou o início do\Nconflito de 400 anos desta terra...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:02.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Watch out! Something's falling again! - Funi}Cuidado! Algo mais está caindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's that? - Funi}{Again...? - Z}E agora...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone, heads down! - Funi}Abaixem-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:09.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma folha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:16.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:19.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem algo escrito nela...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:20.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's a message! - Funi}Uma mensagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{From Luffy and Nami! - Funi}É do Luffy e da Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que diz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:30.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{"Cut down this huge vine\Nso it falls towards the west." - Funi}"Cortem este cipó enorme\Npara que caia pro oeste."
Comment: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:28.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Cut down this huge vine so it falls towards the west."
Comment: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Cut down this huge vine so it falls towards the west."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:37.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Um, what'll happen... if we do that? - Funi}E... qual seria\No objetivo de fazer isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:55.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I've accomplished all my objectives. - Funi}Realizei tudo\No que me propus a fazer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All that's left now is... - Funi}Tudo que resta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:04.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{to destroy this land together with the cumuloregalis clouds using Raigo, - Funi}{\q2}é destruir esta terra e as nuvens\Ncumuloimperator com meu Raigo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:07.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e partir rumo à Endless Vearth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:14.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora que chegou a hora,\Nquase sinto pena de partir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn him! - Funi}Aquele miserável!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That is way bigger than the one from earlier! - Funi}É impressão minha ou esse\Né maior que o anterior...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We... won't be able to escape from this land... - Funi}Nós... podemos esquecer de escapar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{any longer! - Funi}Estamos presos aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:43.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Adeus, Skypiea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's bigger than the last one! That bastard! - Funi}{It's even bigger this time!\NThat bastard! - Z}É ainda maior que da\Núltima vez! Maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. - Funi}Verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora que pegou o sino dourado,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,ele não tem mais nada\Na ver com esta terra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami, você não ia escapar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você espera que eu vá embora agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You want to ring it, right? That golden bell? - Funi}Você quer tocar aquele\Nsino dourado, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É! Eu vou tocá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:13.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Honestly... you can't even control the waver. - Funi}Ah, por favor, você nem\Nconsegue controlar o waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:18.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even if I just leave you here, you'll keep trying to jump anyway, so I'll give you a ride and shoot you up there. - Funi}{\q2}Você vai ficar pulando de qualquer jeito se eu for,\Nentão deixa eu te lançar lá pra cima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:21.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But... - Funi}Em troca...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:27.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{you have to guarantee my life! - Funi}me prometa que eu vou sobreviver!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:30.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Okay, got it! Thanks! - Funi}É, beleza! Valeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.92,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo ainda está lá embaixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:37.13,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're just gonna get one chance, one moment! - Funi}{We only get this\None time to pull it off! - Z}Só temos uma chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:42.63,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I hope they got my message okay. - Funi}Por favor, me digam que receberam\Na minha mensagem lá embaixo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:48.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're gonna jump to the ship by crossing the falling vine?! - Funi}Eles vão pular pro navio usando\No cipó como rampa enquanto cai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:50.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que mais poderia significar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é loucura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then you go up there and stop them. - Funi}Fique à vontade pra subir e pará-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As if he could be stopped! - Funi}Ele não vai parar e você sabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:03.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In any case, reckless or not, we've got no choice but to let him do this! - Funi}Não importa quão imprudente seja,\Ntemos que deixá-lo tentar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Narigudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ah, got 'im! - CR}É, peguei ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If we stay here, we'll be pushed off to the ruins below. - Funi}Vamos cair nas ruínas nesse ritmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone, get away from the vine for now! - Funi}Fiquem longe do cipó por enquanto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fujam pro chão firme!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Anyhow, I'm gonna do it! - Funi}Esse é por minha conta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I need to cut the vine down towards the ship, right?! - Funi}Cortar na direção do navio, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:23.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Mas...!
Comment: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I need to cut the vine down towards the ship, right?!
Comment: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:23.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?! But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:29.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Os únicos nesta ilha do céu que podem\Nalcançar Enel antes daquilo cair...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:32.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,...são aqueles dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's too late to struggle\Nor escape now. - Funi}Nem lutar nem fugir\Nvai te salvar agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You still don't get it? - Funi}Ainda é tão difícil de entender?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:49.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{When you entered the survival game, your fate was already decided. - Funi}Seu destino foi selado quando\Nvocê entrou no jogo de sobrevivência.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:55.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-E-Ele está bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Contamos com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:08:01.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é o único que\Nconsegue derrubar aquilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn you, making all these holes! - Funi}Para de fazer esses buracos, droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Ele cortou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You worms! - Funi}Insetos insignificantes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:43.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:46.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-M-Mas ele conseguiu! Ele cortou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah não...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não está caindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{even though it was cut... - Funi}Mas ele cortou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What a strong vine! - Funi}Que cipó resistente!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:01.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is that thing really a plant?! - Funi}Dá pra ter certeza que é uma planta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que patético...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is what you outsiders get for butting in. - Funi}Como se forasteiros intrometidos\Ntivessem capacidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wyper! Don't be reckless! - Funi}Wyper, não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quieto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:15.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It is important that we, the inheritors of Kalgara's wishes, ring that bell! - Funi}{\q2}Herdamos os desejos de Kalgara, é vital\Nque sejamos nós a tocar aquele sino!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:18.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What does this have to do with that Straw Hat?! - Funi}Chapéu de Palha nunca teve\Nnada a ver com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deixa ele, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:25.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He can't stop us when he's seriously injured like that. Our priority now is knocking over that vine! - Funi}{\q2}Ele está ferido demais pra atrapalhar!\NTemos que focar em derrubar o cipó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Luffy and Nami are waiting up there! - Funi}Luffy e Nami dependem disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:31.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In any case, Zoro cut half of the stem. - Funi}Até agora, Zoro cortou metade do caule...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A coisa toda já deveria\Nestar inclinando.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:37.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{By hitting it with my\NDance of Exploding Stars... - Funi}Quando eu atacar com minha\NDance of Exploding Stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:42.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{it'll be leveled with a loud scream! - Funi}ele vai cair com um grito arrepiante!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:48.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As expected, I am the last line of defense of this pirate group! - Funi}Como sempre, sobrou pra mim levar\Nnossa tripulação até a linha de chegada!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:53.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Robin, take care of those who have fallen! - Funi}Robin, cuide dos nossos aliados caídos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parecem um bolo kashiwa-mochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Move out! - Funi}Toda velocidade à frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:10.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quatrocentos anos atrás, um explorador\Ncontou a mentira de que viu uma cidade de ouro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:16.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Although people laughed at him,\Nhis descendants believed his words... - Funi}{\q2}Embora tenha virado alvo de zombaria,\Nseus descendentes acreditaram nele...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:21.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and are still searching for this city of gold in the Blue Sea. - Funi}e continuam a procurar\Na Cidade do Ouro no Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:33.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se tocarmos o sino dourado,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:37.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,podemos avisá-los de que\Na Cidade do Ouro está no céu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:41.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É isso que aquele\Ngaroto do chapéu de palha pensa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's a wonderful reason, isn't it? - Funi}Que razão melhor poderia haver?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:48.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It has romanticism. - Funi}Isso é romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo numa situação dessas...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:54.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,chegando a perder\Nsua chance de escapar...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's nuts! - Funi}Beira o absurdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:58.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lethal Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:10:59.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Exploding Star Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Usopp's Rubber Band of Doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rolling Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:03.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What... - Funi}Me diga...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{is the name of this explorer's descendant? - Funi}o nome do descendente\Ndeste explorador...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mont Blanc Cricket...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:24.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then is the name... - Funi}Então o ancestral dele\Nde 400 anos atrás...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{of his ancestor from 400 years ago... - Funi}Será que o nome dele é...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:30.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Noland?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:34.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wyper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:38.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What're you doing\Nall of a sudden, Wyper?! - Funi}O que está acontecendo, Wyper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.72,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Será isso um milagre...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:47.94,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Grande Guerreiro Kalgara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.03,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Nola!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:56.90,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Vamos tocar o sino de novo hoje pra que\No som chegue até o fim do céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:12:01.62,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's send the sound that you love to Noland! - Funi}Esse som que você tanto ama...\NVamos enviá-lo a Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que foi aquilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:43.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But to think that this vine wasn't\Naffected by that shock at all... - Funi}Mas é absurdo que o impacto\Nnão moveu o cipó nem um pouco...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:45.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! This time'll be Triple Explo– - Funi}Bem, desta vez será Triple Explo–
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Out of my way! - Funi}Saia da frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Reject!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:12.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What the heck was that?! - Funi}Tá de brincadeira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:13.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que insensato...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:19.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A reject dial... - Funi}Ele usou um reject dial...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:24.20,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Break! Giant Jack! - Funi}Quebre ao meio, Giant Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:37.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está caindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Lá vamos nós! Sobe, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Run it at full power! - Funi}{Go as fast as it'll let you! - Z}Dê tudo que puder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:47.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra ser sincero...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:54.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I've never tried the maximum power of this jet dial... - Funi}essa vai ser a primeira vez que uso\Neste jet dial na potência máxima...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:59.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{because it's too strong for me to control. - Funi}Não vou conseguir controlar\Nalgo tão potente!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:00.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then use it! - Funi}Pra mim tá ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:01.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Lá vamos nós, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:07.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está caindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What on earth is going on?! - Funi}O que diabos está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're counting on you two! Luffy! Nami! - Funi}{It's up to you, Luffy and Nami! - Z}Luffy! Nami! Estamos todos\Ncontando com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:29.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Se a ilha do céu desaparecer agora,\Nnão vamos poder tocar o sino dourado!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você vai tocá-lo, né?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:34.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You'll let old-timer Cricket hear it, right?! - Funi}Vai deixar o Sr. Cricket ouvir, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Jump to where Enel is! - Funi}É melhor você conseguir\Npular pro navio do Enel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo depende de vocês dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ora, ora...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:15:00.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why can't you quietly wait for the completion of Raigo? - Funi}Por que não ficam quietos\Ne esperam meu Raigo terminar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How impatient they are... - Funi}Que impaciência insolente...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então não tenho escolha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:19.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's insolent of you to try and come to me! - Funi}É pura insolência\Ntentar me alcançar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:22.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês precisam de uma lição!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Mamaragan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele maldito...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's trying to sink\Nthe vine from the base! - Funi}Ele está tentando afundar o cipó\Ndestruindo sua base!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Faz alguma coisa, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I can't do anything! - Funi}{What can I possibly do?! - Z}O que eu deveria fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Já estamos subindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:49.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If this vine loses its foundation, we'll no longer be able to come up this high! - Funi}Não vamos subir o bastante se ele\Ndestruir a base do cipó!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We won't be able to get close to Enel! - Funi}Vamos ficar abaixo de Enel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Upper Yard is being pummeled with attacks! - Funi}{Upper Yard is taking\Na real pummeling! - Z}Upper Yard está sendo bombardeada!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even if the lightning doesn't work on you, - Funi}Não me importa se você é\Nimune a raios!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{it doesn't mean anything unless you can reach here! - Funi}Não vai adiantar nada\Nse você não chegar aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:19.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Fall down below and wait for the completion of Raigo, rubber man! - Funi}Despence lá pra baixo e aguarde\No Raigo, homem de borracha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:31.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Upper Yard está... sendo pulverizada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:37.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:38.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:46.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Looks like he doesn't want to come in contact with you ever again, huh? - Funi}Ele realmente quer manter\Ndistância de você, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Not a chance! - Funi}Quero ver ele tentar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:54.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The ruins are being exposed! - Funi}Está expondo as ruínas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:01.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He intends to pulverize the ground. - Funi}Esses ataques vão\Ndestruir a fundação.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wyper's lying on the ground down there! - Funi}Wyper acabou no\Nchão lá embaixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro também!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Filho da mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As ruínas...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É inútil, Enel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You can't bring down... - Funi}Você não pode apagar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,W-Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:35.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{...the history of the proud warriors who lived in the land of Shandia. - Funi}...a história dos orgulhosos guerreiros\Nque viveram em Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:47.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No matter where it is, this grand power is strong, creates and nurtures. - Funi}Seja aqui ou em qualquer lugar, seu grande\Npoder pode criar e nutrir...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You just can't bring it down! - Funi}Derrubar não é tão fácil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:54.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No matter how many forests you burn... - Funi}Não importa quantas florestas\Nvocê queime...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:59.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No matter how many ruins you destroy... - Funi}Não importa quantas ruínas\Nvocê destrua...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:05.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The land won't be beaten! - Funi}Esta terra vai perseverar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Saia daí, Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.45,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,É perigoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wyper vai morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:22.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me solta, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:23.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:26.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I can still hear driveling from below. - Funi}A tagarelice lá de baixo não para.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:07.21,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Vearth is... That's right! - Funi}E se a vearth...? Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não está afundando!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:22.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Upper Yard wasn't affected at all! - Funi}Upper Yard se manteve inteira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que poder incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:34.28,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:37.28,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Vearth is so grand! - Funi}{Vearth is simply amazing! - Z}Vearth é absolutamente magnífica!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:45.04,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Vearth wasn't something to fight over, - Funi}Vearth nunca foi algo\Npelo qual se deveria lutar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:50.42,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{but the blood of many people was shed, and many lives were lost. - Funi}{and yet there was much bloodshed\Nwith many losing their lives over it. - Z}e mesmo assim tanto sangue foi\Nderramado e tantas vidas perdidas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:55.30,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why didn't we notice it for 400 years?! - Funi}Como pudemos ser tão cegos\Npor 400 anos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:06.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Get out! The vine is falling! - Funi}Saiam! O cipó está caindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Come over here, now! - Funi}Venham pra cá, agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:25.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:31.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Here I come! Enel! - Funi}Lá vou eu, Enel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:34.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're a bunch of... - Funi}A insolência de\Ncada um deles...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:39.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hand over the golden bell! - Funi}Devolva aquele sino dourado!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Enough of this! - Funi}Já chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:42.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou farto de você!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I think this is big enough. - Funi}Já cresceu o bastante...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desapareça junto com a terra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:55.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Raigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami, thanks! - Funi}Valeu, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:16.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:19.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's no way I'll let\Nyour help go to waste! - Funi}Não vou deixar sua ajuda ser em vão!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:23.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The ship is that way! - Funi}O navio é pro outro lado!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:36.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Luffy! There's an eddy of\Nair and lightning in there! - Funi}Luffy! Aquilo é um vórtice\Nde ar e raios!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:38.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem sabe o que vai acontecer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:45.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What can you do before this huge power, rubber man?! - Funi}O que pode fazer contra\Nesse poder, homem de borracha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:17.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:25.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Fireworks!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.65,0:22:25.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\alpha&HFF&}Fireworks!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:21.95,0:22:25.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\alpha&HFF&}Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Golden Peony!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:47.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How dare you use thunder to create bad weather for the idyllic sky islands?! - Funi}{Your thunder is making a mess of\Nthe weather on these nice sky islands! - Z}{\q2}O clima da ilha era tão bom antes de você\Nestragar com seus raios estúpidos!
Comment: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:42.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How dare you use thunder to create bad weather for the idyllic sky islands?!
Comment: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:44.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How dare you use thunder to create bad weather for the idyllic sky islands?!
Comment: 0,0:22:44.68,0:22:47.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How dare you use thunder to create bad weather for the idyllic sky islands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:49.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu maníaco dos raios!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:55.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What is this abnormal\Nelectric discharge?! - Funi}Q-O que está acontecendo com\Na descarga elétrica?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.61,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:03.57,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{He has gold, which can transmit electricity, on his hand! - Funi}O ouro na mão dele é\No condutor perfeito pra eletricidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:09.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, all I have to do is drop it before the electricity completely discharges! - Funi}Muito bem! Vou largá-lo antes\Nde toda a eletricidade descarregar!
Comment: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:06.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well, all I have to do is drop it before the electricity completely discharges!
Comment: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:09.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well, all I have to do is drop it before the electricity completely discharges!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:13.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everything... be gone! - Funi}Desapareçam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:18.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitão McKinley!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:20.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor, pare.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:21.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is God's Land. - Funi}Aqui é a Terra de Deus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:23.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's pointless! - Funi}Não tem sentido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não me importa se não tem sentido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:30.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's nothing else humans can do when the situation is life or death! - Funi}O que mais as pessoas podem fazer numa\Nsituação de vida ou morte?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:34.81,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Para sobreviver,\Nescolhemos abandonar nossa terra.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:39.31,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now we've lost a place to return to and our way forward. - Funi}Não podemos voltar e\Nnão podemos avançar...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:44.11,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo que podemos fazer é rezar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:54.33,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{When we hear the "island's singing voice," this battle will end. - Funi}Quando ouvirmos a "canção\Nda ilha," essa batalha vai acabar.
Comment: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:47.07,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,When we hear the "island's singing voice," this battle will end.
Comment: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:54.33,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,When we hear the "island's singing voice," this battle will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:24:01.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if no one will survive at this point... - Funi}Será que ainda haverá\Nsobreviventes a essa altura...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:06.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if, had I had the courage to stand up to Enel... - Funi}Se eu tivesse tido coragem de\Nenfrentar Enel, será que...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:10.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't have had to involve those people... - Funi}teria sido necessário\Nenvolvê-los...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:13.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Suu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:18.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if God exists? - Funi}Será que realmente existe um deus...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:22.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se existir, será que ele nos salvaria...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.24,0:24:28.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor... se você realmente existe...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.57,0:24:32.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,por favor, proteja-os, Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.41,0:24:35.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor... faça um milagre acontecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.62,0:24:39.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Protect this land! God! - Funi}Por favor, Deus, proteja esta terra!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.76,0:24:54.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Limpe-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.49,0:25:14.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The mass of thunderclouds has disappeared! - Funi}A massa de nuvens de trovão sumiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.41,0:25:18.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.42,0:25:22.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.52,0:25:39.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Luffy! - Funi}Isso aí, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.94,0:25:52.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Straw Hat! - Funi}Toque, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.32,0:25:55.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ring the Light of Shandora! - Funi}Brilhem a Luz de Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.37,0:25:57.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.49,0:26:01.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let us hear the singing voice of the island! - Funi}Deixe-nos ouvir a canção da ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.12,0:26:08.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How dare you destroy Raigo?! You monkey from the Blue Sea! - Funi}{How dare a Blue Sea monkey\Ndestroy my Raigo?! - Z}Como ousa destruir meu Raigo,\Nseu maldito macaco do Blue Sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.17,0:26:11.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well then, I'll ring you as well! - Funi}Que tal se eu te tocar também?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.51,0:26:14.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You insolent brat! - Funi}Seu miserável insolente!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.06,0:26:19.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}200 Milhões...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.93,0:26:21.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Volts:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.39,0:26:24.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Amaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.40,0:26:28.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que diabo é aquilo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.73,0:26:30.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{"Ring," you said?! - Funi}"Tocar," é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.65,0:26:32.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You mean the golden bell?! - Funi}Tocar o sino dourado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.95,0:26:37.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The next time it rings,\Nit will be the end of the battle. - Funi}Seu próximo soar vai sinalizar\No fim desta batalha!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.53,0:26:41.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you trying to hang onto such a legend?! - Funi}De que adianta se agarrar\Na lendas obsoletas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.75,0:26:43.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.55,0:26:54.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You are just a paramecia! - Funi}Você é apenas um tipo paramecia!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.47,0:27:01.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's no way that I can't crush you with my logia power! - Funi}Meus poderes logia garantem\Nminha capacidade de te esmagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.10,0:27:06.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I said it doesn't work on me! - Funi}{And again, that doesn't work on me! - Z}Já te disse que\Nisso não funciona em mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.02,0:27:10.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm sick of this "I'm God" crap! - Funi}"Deus" isso! "Deus" aquilo! Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.73,0:27:14.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What god wouldn't save anything at all?! - Funi}Que tipo de deus\Nse recusa a salvar alguma coisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.58,0:27:26.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.71,0:27:29.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você se agarrou nele\Npra não ser espetado, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.84,0:27:31.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.88,0:27:37.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What are you going to do, rubber man?! You have nowhere to escape! - Funi}Qual é seu próximo passo, homem de borracha?!\NNão tem pra onde fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.18,0:27:43.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The pull of your arm will make the spear dig deeper and deeper into you! - Funi}Quanto mais esticar o braço,\Na lança vai te perfurar mais fundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.22,0:27:46.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yet, if you get away, you'll fall! - Funi}E se escapar disso\Nvai cair!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.61,0:27:52.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You've done well to climb up this high! - Funi}Devo te parabenizar\Npor subir tão alto!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.03,0:27:56.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{However, this is the end of you and this land, too! - Funi}Porém, é até aqui que você vai,\Ne esta terra também acabou!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.91,0:27:58.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I can create another Raigo! - Funi}Vou criar quantos Raigos forem necessários!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.95,0:28:05.71,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{It is our citizens' duty... - Funi}Este é nosso dever como cidadãos.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.92,0:28:08.33,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry! - Funi}Me desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.42,0:28:13.50,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.42,0:28:17.30,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,A ilha do céu vai...\Ndesaparecer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.47,0:28:26.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então você escolheu cair!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.44,0:28:34.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.19,0:28:38.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami! Sai da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.49,0:28:44.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-O que você...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.25,0:28:48.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não brinca comigo, orelhas!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.08,0:28:52.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.00,0:28:57.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.88,0:29:01.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you trying again?! - Funi}Outra tentativa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.80,0:29:04.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Até o sino tocar!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.47,0:29:06.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This time, I'll skewer you! - Funi}Vai ser espetado\Ncom certeza desta vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.64,0:29:09.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{...Gold Rifle! - Funi}...Golden Rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.73,0:29:14.48,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's too fast! - Funi}Rápido demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.08,0:29:35.42,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Quando você voltar a Jaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.30,0:29:39.13,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{what will you think when\Nyou see we're gone? - Funi}o que vai pensar\Nquando ver que partimos?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.76,0:29:44.14,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hold on a little longer! I'll let you know... - Funi}Aguente mais um pouco!\NVou enviar a mensagem de que...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.76,0:29:48.22,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1020)}{that "we are here"! - Funi}{that we are here! - Z}nós estamos aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.86,0:29:57.19,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Light the fire of Shandora! - Funi}Brilhem a Luz de Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.49,0:30:04.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Já se passaram 400 anos desde\Nque a batalha no céu começou.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.24,0:30:09.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Só uma vez, nós queríamos...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.62,0:30:13.37,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,978)}Isso mesmo. A terra sagrada vai...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.79,0:30:19.84,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,cantar de novo...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.26,0:30:27.93,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,um dia, com certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.94,0:30:45.99,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Seis anos atrás, vi uma enorme cidade de ouro\Nna ilha de Jaya na Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.37,0:30:53.54,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{The City of Gold does exist! - Funi}A Cidade do Ouro existe! Eu juro!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.59,0:31:08.85,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Ninguém jamais refutou a existência\Nda Cidade do Ouro ou da ilha do céu.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.26,0:31:12.02,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,267)}Isso é romance!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.02,0:31:16.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Reach! - Funi}Agora alcance!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.65,0:31:17.48,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Old guy! - Funi}Cabeça de castanha!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.15,0:31:19.40,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Você consegue ouvir?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.65,0:31:22.74,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,A Cidade do Ouro está aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.78,0:31:26.11,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Por 400 anos...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.91,0:31:28.62,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{the City of Gold has\Nbeen here all this time... - Funi}a Cidade do Ouro esteve aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.20,0:31:37.88,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,no céu!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=11}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=12}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
